### Ask a Question on an Ad
# Submits a new question on an ad listing.
# The caller must not be the ad owner (seller cannot ask on own ad).
# Rate limits: max 3 unanswered questions per user per ad, 5-min cooldown.
#
# @name askQuestion
POST {{host}}/api/qa/ads/{{adId}}/questions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "text": "Is this item available for international shipping?"
}

###

### Submit an Answer to a Question
# Submits an answer to a question. The type (SELLER or COMMUNITY) is
# automatically determined:
# - If the caller is the ad owner → SELLER answer
# - If the caller has a completed purchase on the ad → COMMUNITY answer
# - Otherwise → 403 ANSWER_NOT_PREVIOUS_BUYER
#
# @name submitAnswer
POST {{host}}/api/qa/questions/{{questionId}}/answers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "text": "Yes, we ship internationally. Shipping costs depend on the destination."
}

###

### Edit an Answer
# Edits an existing answer. Only the answer author can edit.
#
# @name editAnswer
PUT {{host}}/api/qa/answers/{{answerId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "text": "Yes, we ship internationally to most countries. Contact us for a shipping quote."
}

###

### Toggle Upvote on a Question
# Toggles the upvote status of a question for the authenticated user.
# If already upvoted, the upvote is removed. Otherwise, it is added.
#
# @name toggleUpvote
POST {{host}}/api/qa/questions/{{questionId}}/upvote
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### Toggle Pin on a Question (Seller Only)
# Toggles the pin status of a question. Only the ad owner can pin.
# Maximum 3 pinned questions per ad.
#
# @name togglePin
PUT {{host}}/api/qa/questions/{{questionId}}/pin
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### Hide a Question (Seller Only)
# Hides a question from public view. Only the ad owner can hide.
# Hidden questions are no longer visible in public listings.
#
# @name hideQuestion
PUT {{host}}/api/qa/questions/{{questionId}}/hide
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### Remove a Question (Admin Only)
# Permanently removes a question. Admin/moderator action only.
#
# @name removeQuestion
DELETE {{host}}/api/qa/questions/{{questionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### Get Seller's Unanswered Questions
# Returns unanswered (pending) questions for the seller's ad.
# The caller must be the ad owner.
#
# @name getSellerUnanswered
GET {{host}}/api/qa/ads/{{adId}}/questions/seller?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### Get My Unanswered Questions on an Ad
# Returns the caller's own unanswered (pending) questions on an ad.
#
# @name getMyUnanswered
GET {{host}}/api/qa/ads/{{adId}}/questions/mine
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
